---
// 全站最底层背景装饰：两侧纵向流动光束（参考 composio.dev）。纯 CSS，不参与布局/交互。
---
<div class="rails" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="rails-glow"></div>
  <div class="rails-grid"></div>
  <div class="rail rail-left">
    <span class="rail-line"></span><span class="rail-line rail-line-2"></span>
    <i class="beam b1"></i><i class="beam b2"></i><i class="beam b3"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="rail rail-right">
    <span class="rail-line"></span><span class="rail-line rail-line-2"></span>
    <i class="beam b1"></i><i class="beam b2"></i><i class="beam b3"></i>
  </div>
</div>
